0.312+08:00\",\"hostname\":\"halei-Surface-Pro-4\",\"message\":\"tools.allow allowlist contains unknown entries (taskflow, acp-router, channel-feishu, feishu). These entries won't match any tool unless the plugin is enabled.\",\"traceId\":\"06bf8f512f4a2c3f90eb161ff7560b7e\",\"spanId\":\"1f7067623d3a5716\",\"traceFlags\":\"01\"}\n{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"agent/embedded\\\"}\",\"1\":\"[tools] No callable tools remain after resolving explicit tool allowlist (tools.allow: taskflow, acp-router, channel-feishu, feishu); no registered tools matched. Fix the allowlist or enable the plugin that registers the requested tool.\",\"_meta\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.2\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"agent/embedded\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-05-03T10:55:40.930Z\",\"logLevelId\":4,\"logLevelName\":\"WARN\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Bhq-McUP.js:150:14\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-Bhq-McUP.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-Bhq-McUP.js:150\",\"fileColumn\":\"14\",\"fileLine\":\"150\",\"filePath\":\".npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Bhq-McUP.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\".npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-Bhq-McUP.js:150\",\"method\":\"logToFile\"}},\"time\":\"2026-05-03T18:55:40.934+08:00\",\"hostname\":\"halei-Surface-Pro-4\",\"message\":\"[tools] No callable tools remain after resolving explicit tool allowlist (tools.allow: taskflow, acp-router, channel-feishu, feishu); no registered tools matched. Fix the allowlist or enable the plugin that registers the requested tool.\",\"traceId\":\"06bf8f512f4a2c3f90eb161ff7560b7e\",\"spanId\":\"1f7067623d3a5716\",\"traceFlags\":\"01\"}\n{\"0\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"agent/embedded\\\"}\",\"1\":{\"event\":\"embedded_run_failover_decision\",\"tags\":[\"error_handling\",\"failover\",\"prompt\",\"surface_error\"],\"runId\":\"3e4e1c2e-6f27-4a45-b12d-c