{"type":"message","id":"88258caf","parentId":"cd8d74aa","timestamp":"2026-05-03T12:47:58.554Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Messages from 飞书 are not arriving. The user wants to know if 飞书 messages should route to the current webchat conversation.\n\nFrom the runtime metadata I can see:\n- channel: webchat\n- provider: webchat\n- surface: webchat\n- chat_type: direct\n\nSo this is a webchat session. The 飞书 messages should be routing somewhere - either to this same webchat or to a different session. \n\nThe issue is likely that 飞书 is configured but not properly routed to this webchat session. Or perhaps the 飞书 plugin needs to be properly connected.\n\nLet me check the current config to see how channels are set up. But I don't have a tool to read config directly without exec...\n\nActually I should just acknowledge - I haven't seen any 飞书 messages come through. The user is asking if they should arrive here. They should, if the routing is configured correctly. But since I'm in webchat mode, 飞书 messages might be going to a different session or channel.\n\nLet me just answer the user honestly.","thinkingSignature":"892744384e58efb8d16c7f4adb64c662e9f9c8e3d07b051a128093ba1ace5d56"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v05e1w8x35e1_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":223,"output":234,"cacheRead":27552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28009,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777812459655,"responseId":"064676ebcd323d77a4714802b781433a"}}
