{"type":"message","id":"127dbff1","parentId":"85def2c5","timestamp":"2026-05-03T12:57:21.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they are chatting with me via web UI, not using any channel. So feishu messages won't reach me directly - I need to check if feishu is properly configured as a channel. The user sent messages from feishu but they came to this web UI session. This suggests feishu integration may be working but routing messages to the web UI session instead of a dedicated feishu session.\n\nLet me ask what they need - they seem to be confirming that communication is working via web UI. They're saying they use web UI to talk to me, no channel. So maybe the question is whether feishu messages route here?\n\nActually re-reading: \"我的用webui端给你通话，没有用任何channel\" - they're saying they use web UI to talk to me, not any channel. So feishu isn't connected as a channel - that's why feishu messages don't reach me.\n\nLet me just confirm and ask what they need help with.","thinkingSignature":"5f3ae0ef8971f018bd469695c4b5b58b55f7f2360400c9e7d1b9b9719752d19b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_534n08vgjhvl_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30649,"output":214,"cacheRead":32,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30895,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777813033362,"responseId":"0646792a4b2df1846551488cfd9e9f2d"}}
