{"type":"message","id":"4fa305da","parentId":"c58e5358","timestamp":"2026-05-03T12:58:44.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to set up the Feishu integration. They've been trying to get Feishu working. Let me check what needs to be done. \n\nLooking at the conversation:\n1. User tried to configure tools.profile to minimal and restart\n2. Then they wanted to install Feishu CLI\n3. They selected \"机器人身份\" (bot-only identity)\n4. They went through the binding process\n5. After restart, they tried sending messages from Feishu but couldn't receive them\n6. They're using web UI to chat with me, not any channel\n\nThe issue is that Feishu is configured but messages from Feishu aren't routing to the current conversation. This is a routing/channel configuration issue.\n\nLet me think about what needs to be set up:\n1. The Feishu CLI is installed and configured (bot identity)\n2. OpenClaw needs to have the Feishu channel properly configured to receive messages and route them to the agent\n\nThe user is using web UI directly, but wants Feishu to work too. The issue might be that:\n1. The Feishu channel plugin isn't properly configured in OpenClaw's config\n2. The Feishu webhook or callback isn't set up correctly\n\nLet me check the current OpenClaw config to see what Feishu-related configuration exists.","thinkingSignature":"a50a467cb0ddc24369840906392b1ad924db4631cad3863ca735f463761b83cc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8cpdr1ojajdm_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":289,"cacheRead":31072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31415,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777813115728,"responseId":"0646797dec80ffc6e38e67b7678426cd"}}
