{"type":"message","id":"f8469172","parentId":"b4a0c3cd","timestamp":"2026-05-03T13:51:14.586Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the gateway is restarting repeatedly. Based on the logs, yes - the gateway has been restarting frequently. The service unit has Restart=always, and there have been many restarts. The \"channel stop exceeded 5000ms after abort\" messages suggest channels are timing out during shutdown, causing rapid restarts.\n\nLet me check the current gateway status and also look at what might be causing the repeated restarts.","thinkingSignature":"743f2b92ddf58da7edaebcb8297fc13cf8fdc8e5058dc67a24f04d14031772bf"},{"type":"text","text":"是的。从日志看有两个问题：\n\n1. **飞书 channel shutdown 超时** — \"channel stop exceeded 5000ms after abort\"，每次关机要等 5 秒才强制结束，导致频繁重启\n2. **事件循环严重阻塞** — eventLoopDelayMaxMs 达到 2000ms+，CPU 跑满\n\n让我查一下当前网关是否存活：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nwgbhzbpijqg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"systemctl --user status openclaw-gateway 2>&1 | head -15","yieldMs":5000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":218,"cacheRead":86518,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86736,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777816265540,"responseId":"064685cb6b40af2fcc6d7a7457d71bed"}}
