bash --noprofile --norc -c \"systemctl --user status openclaw-gateway 2>&1 | head -15\"\n             ├─91923 systemctl --user status openclaw-gateway\n             └─91924 head -15\n\n5月 03 21:50:46 halei-Surface-Pro-4 node[91815]: 2026-05-03T21:50:46.282+08:00 [ws] ⇄ res ✓ sessions.list 23954ms conn=eee09d70…2d6f id=d3a8bb63…a79d\n5月 03 21:50:50 halei-Surface-Pro-4 node[91815]: 2026-05-03T21:50:50.786+08:00 [ws] ⇄ res ✓ sessions.list 9883ms conn=c9a198ab…ab8c id=1df7b7ce…dc89","cwd":"/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777816276331}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba83cf98","parentId":"ad19bbd5","timestamp":"2026-05-03T13:51:29.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the gateway is now running (since 21:50:09). I can see sessions.list calls taking 23954ms and 9883ms - that's very slow! The gateway is responding but very slowly. This is a performance issue.\n\nNow let me test if the gateway is accessible:","thinkingSignature":"719b29c107b3beb64633550192f3a3c4393752f86d9012dd7ff3065c4d3b4e4e"},{"type":"text","text":"网关现在跑起来了。但刚才日志里 sessions.list 响应用了 23954ms — 非常慢。\n\n测试通信：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wrnr1jx2v7az_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":5,"messageLimit":2,"includeLastMessage":true}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66175,"output":136,"cacheRead":20974,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777816276346,"responseId":"064685d586fd83e55673aae698ef8540"}}
